00:50:54,840 --> 00:50:55,380
 Mihael,

1199
00:50:55,380 --> 00:50:56,700
 Gabriela,

1200
00:50:56,700 --> 00:50:57,580
 Rafaela,

1201
00:50:57,580 --> 00:50:58,120
 Tina

1202
00:50:58,120 --> 00:50:59,600
 i ja tamo onaj.

1203
00:50:59,600 --> 00:51:01,860
 On jednom putu

1204
00:51:01,860 --> 00:51:03,020
 slikano.

1205
00:51:03,020 --> 00:51:04,680
 I sad sa ovim Davido,

1206
00:51:04,680 --> 00:51:06,040
 našim najmanjim tamo,

1207
00:51:06,040 --> 00:51:07,180
 smo imali

1208
00:51:07,180 --> 00:51:08,600
 i imamo još,

1209
00:51:08,600 --> 00:51:10,040
 ali puno bolja situacija,

1210
00:51:10,040 --> 00:51:11,860
 jednu borbu za zdravlje.

1211
00:51:11,860 --> 00:51:14,060
 Za slobodu za zdravlje.

1212
00:51:14,060 --> 00:51:19,120
 I nije pitanje pobjede

1213
00:51:19,120 --> 00:51:21,820
 je li on do kraja ozdravio ili nije.

1214
00:51:21,820 --> 00:51:23,460
 Pitanje pobjede je

1215
00:51:23,460 --> 00:51:26,260
 da je naš život puno više

1216
00:51:26,260 --> 00:51:28,040
 u karizmi zajedništva,

1217
00:51:28,040 --> 00:51:29,520
 općenito,

1218
00:51:29,520 --> 00:51:30,560
 u svemu.

1219
00:51:30,560 --> 00:51:32,140
 To je pobjeda.

1220
00:51:32,140 --> 00:51:34,800
 Da smo dublje zagazili na putu

1221
00:51:34,800 --> 00:51:36,740
 slobode za ljubav.

1222
00:51:36,740 --> 00:51:39,380
 I međusobno kao obitelj

1223
00:51:39,380 --> 00:51:42,520
 i pobjeda da smo bili svjedočanstvo

1224
00:51:42,520 --> 00:51:43,520
 mnogima.

1225
00:51:43,520 --> 00:51:44,680
 Bili smo u New Yorku

1226
00:51:44,680 --> 00:51:45,900
 gdje je nastala ova knjiga.

1227
00:51:46,340 --> 00:51:48,380
 nastala je ili u šest popovodne,

1228
00:51:48,380 --> 00:51:50,520
 tamo je po onoću Hrvatskoj.

1229
00:51:50,520 --> 00:51:52,340
 I onda sve zaspe,

1230
00:51:52,340 --> 00:51:54,160
 ovo više ne zvnza,

1231
00:51:54,160 --> 00:51:57,300
 i ti nas spremala diplomski,

1232
00:51:57,300 --> 00:51:58,860
 iz logoterapije,

1233
00:51:58,860 --> 00:52:01,260
 ja sam pisao knjigu.

1234
00:52:01,260 --> 00:52:03,140
 Tako je nastala.

1235
00:52:03,140 --> 00:52:04,700
 To je još jedna pobjeda.

1236
00:52:04,700 --> 00:52:06,380
 To je još jedna pobjeda.

1237
00:52:06,380 --> 00:52:08,020
 Ovaj alat za sve nas.

1238
00:52:08,020 --> 00:52:09,940
 Već to sam ja napisao,

1239
00:52:09,940 --> 00:52:11,360
 bilo ko da je napisao.

1240
00:52:11,360 --> 00:52:12,080
 To je pobjeda.

1241
00:52:12,080 --> 00:52:13,460
 To je pobjeda.

1242
00:52:13,460 --> 00:52:16,140
 Da promijenimo tu perspektivu

1243
00:52:16,140 --> 00:52:17,620
 koja nam pomalo svijet nameće.

1244
00:52:17,620 --> 00:52:18,860
 Hoćemo li prestat tražiti

1245
00:52:18,860 --> 00:52:20,140
 čudesa da nestane metal?

1246
00:52:20,140 --> 00:52:21,220
 Ja prvi neću.

1247
00:52:21,220 --> 00:52:23,000
 Nije to ugušt.

1248
00:52:23,000 --> 00:52:24,620
 To mi je slavno inspirira

1249
00:52:24,620 --> 00:52:25,800
 ta čudesa da vidim

1250
00:52:25,800 --> 00:52:27,260
 da je Bog živ,

1251
00:52:27,260 --> 00:52:29,220
 da se stvaraju organi

1252
00:52:29,220 --> 00:52:29,980
 gdje nije bilo.

1253
00:52:29,980 --> 00:52:31,680
 Ali je li to moja pobjeda?

1254
00:52:31,680 --> 00:52:32,220
 Ne.

1255
00:52:32,600 --> 00:52:33,360
 Moja pobjeda je

1256
00:52:33,360 --> 00:52:35,500
 kad su ljudi različiti rasa

1257
00:52:35,500 --> 00:52:37,100
 i različiti vjera

1258
00:52:37,100 --> 00:52:38,820
 došli u toj poliklinici

1259
00:52:38,820 --> 00:52:41,000
 i došla ovih glavni iz poliklinike

1260
00:52:41,000 --> 00:52:41,380
 i kaže

1261
00:52:41,380 --> 00:52:42,680
 pogledajte ove roditelje.

1262
00:52:42,680 --> 00:52:44,200
 Pa ovo je svjedočanstvo ljubavi.

1263
00:52:44,200 --> 00:52:45,880
 Došli su ovde po godine

1264
00:52:45,880 --> 00:52:48,740
 se boriti za zdravlje svog djeteta.

1265
00:52:48,740 --> 00:52:49,820
 I kažemo

1266
00:52:49,820 --> 00:52:50,960
 Bog nam daje snage

1267
00:52:50,960 --> 00:52:51,780
 i Isus je s nama.

1268
00:52:51,780 --> 00:52:53,720
 To je pobjeda ljudi moji.

1269
00:52:53,720 --> 00:52:55,600
 Gotova za okružena teletesta

1270
00:52:55,600 --> 00:52:56,560
 i ostavljena nama.

1271
00:52:56,560 --> 00:52:58,400
 Na putu smo ljubavi

1272
00:52:58,400 --> 00:53:01,300
 da svi budu jedna.

1273
00:53:02,060 --> 00:53:02,700
 Hržište?

1274
00:53:02,700 --> 00:53:03,920
 To je put.

1275
00:53:03,920 --> 00:53:04,780
 To je hod.

1276
00:53:04,780 --> 00:53:06,160
 Haleluja.

1277
00:53:06,160 --> 00:53:07,180
 Haleluja.

1278
00:53:16,820 --> 00:53:19,140
 Tako da to bude sloboda naša.

1279
00:53:19,140 --> 00:53:20,260
 Da bude naša sloboda

1280
00:53:20,260 --> 00:53:21,120
 da ne bude, evo ga,

1281
00:53:21,120 --> 00:53:22,440
 ili zdravlje, ili ništa.

1282
00:53:22,440 --> 00:53:23,780
 Ne.

1283
00:53:23,780 --> 00:53:24,940
 Isus na križu,

1284
00:53:24,940 --> 00:53:25,700
 na govor i drugo.

1285
00:53:25,700 --> 00:53:28,000
 Pozvalo vi još isto

1286
00:53:28,000 --> 00:53:29,460
 za jedno kratko svjedočanstvo

1287
00:53:29,460 --> 00:53:29,980
 o knjizi.

1288
00:53:29,980 --> 00:53:31,800
 Koliko je, evo,

1289
00:53:31,800 --> 00:53:34,520
 ona utjecala već do sada

1290
00:53:34,520 --> 00:53:35,560
 na neke ljude.

1291
00:53:35,560 --> 00:53:37,980
 Jedna žena koja je radila na njoj,

1292
00:53:37,980 --> 00:53:38,820
 to nije Anita,

1293
00:53:39,540 --> 00:53:40,960
 je, kada će sad govoriti,

1294
00:53:40,960 --> 00:53:41,980
 je rekla,

1295
00:53:41,980 --> 00:53:43,540
 ja, šta si mi učinio,

1296
00:53:43,540 --> 00:53:45,640
 morala sam zamoliti

1297
00:53:45,640 --> 00:53:47,400
 administratora WhatsApp grupe

1298
00:53:47,400 --> 00:53:48,700
 u kojoj ima brdo ljudi

1299
00:53:48,700 --> 00:53:50,660
 da se vrati natrag u tu grupu

1300
00:53:50,660 --> 00:53:52,480
 i svima sam se istričavala.

1301
00:53:52,480 --> 00:53:55,560
 Kaže, joj, koja bi je to bila žutva?

1302
00:53:55,560 --> 00:53:56,340
 Ali učinila sam,

1303
00:53:56,340 --> 00:53:57,200
 nisam mogla, kaže,

1304
00:53:57,200 --> 00:53:58,720
 spavala dok li nisam izmirila

1305
00:53:58,720 --> 00:54:00,500
 sa svima što sam mogla se izmirit

1306
00:54:00,500 --> 00:54:02,280
 i ući u tu karizmu, evo.

1307
00:54:02,280 --> 00:54:05,500
 Anita je sa Petrom Jurčevićom

1308
00:54:05,500 --> 00:54:07,040
 koji nije mogao bio ode sa nama,

1309
00:54:07,040 --> 00:54:08,080
 koji ga pozdravljamo,

1310
00:54:08,080 --> 00:54:10,720
 koji je zamjenik koordinatora

1311
00:54:10,720 --> 00:54:11,840
 Nike Rončevića,

1312
00:54:11,840 --> 00:54:13,580
 njegova supruga,

1313
00:54:13,580 --> 00:54:16,500
 oni su obitac Petra Djece.

1314
00:54:20,660 --> 00:54:28,100
 Evo jedno svjedočanstvo njeva.

1315
00:54:28,100 --> 00:54:30,000
 Napisala sam šalabakter.

1316
00:54:30,000 --> 00:54:33,380
 Mi u Dalmac imajmo jednu izreku

1317
00:54:33,380 --> 00:54:34,740
 ZOVI ČOVIKA.

1318
00:54:34,740 --> 00:54:40,160
 Pa sad, kad je napisa knjigu,

1319
00:54:40,160 --> 00:54:42,240
 sam možemo reći ČITAJTE ČOVIKA.

1320
00:54:42,240 --> 00:54:46,100
 Jer Lordan je stvarno osoba

1321
00:54:46,100 --> 00:54:48,300
 u našoj koordinaciji,

1322
00:54:48,300 --> 00:54:49,700
 a je u našoj obitelji,

1323
00:54:49,780 --> 00:54:51,440
 u široj obitelji, u zajednici,

1324
00:54:51,440 --> 00:54:53,880
 koju uvijek možeš nazvati, pitati

1325
00:54:53,880 --> 00:54:55,560
 i reći mu,

1326
00:54:55,560 --> 00:54:57,260
 Lordane, treba mi utiha,

1327
00:54:57,260 --> 00:54:58,180
 treba mi savije,

1328
00:54:58,180 --> 00:54:59,280
 treba mi ohrabrenje,

1329
00:54:59,280 --> 00:55:01,220
 treba mi tvoj pogled izvana.

1330
00:55:01,220 --> 00:55:03,940
 I drago mi da je on napisao u knjigu,

1331
00:55:03,940 --> 00:55:06,420
 da je sabrao sva ta iskustva,

1332
00:55:06,420 --> 00:55:07,680
 sva koja je skupljao.

1333
00:55:07,680 --> 00:55:10,000
 I ja bih sad volila da mu date

1334
00:55:10,000 --> 00:55:12,660
 dan pljesak za sve ono što je on činio

1335
00:55:12,660 --> 00:55:14,480
 sve ove godine kao koordinator

1336
00:55:14,480 --> 00:55:16,480
 ovdje za našu obnovu

1337
00:55:16,480 --> 00:55:18,160
 u Hrvatskoj i Bosni i Hercegovini.

1338
00:55:18,900 --> 00:55:39,720
 Karezmu zajedništva ne može napisat netko,

1339
00:55:39,720 --> 00:55:41,940
 tko ne zna što je karizma zajedništva,

1340
00:55:42,060 --> 00:55:44,280
 a vjerujem to duboko da Lordan zna

1341
00:55:44,280 --> 00:55:47,000
 živeći najprije ono zajedništvo s Bogom,

1342
00:55:47,000 --> 00:55:48,540
 onda u svojoj obitelji,

1343
00:55:48,540 --> 00:55:50,860
 a onda i to proširio na sve nas,

1344
00:55:50,860 --> 00:55:52,880
 na cijelu zajednicu i koordinaciju

1345
00:55:52,880 --> 00:55:54,940
 i vjerujem da ste svi osjetili

1346
00:55:54,940 --> 00:55:57,080
 stvarno tu ljubav koja dolazi

1347
00:55:57,080 --> 00:55:58,700
 iz dubine njegovog srca.

1348
00:55:58,700 --> 00:56:01,300
 Ja sam, ja vam nisam evangelizator,

1349
00:56:01,300 --> 00:56:02,100
 to je moj muž,

1350
00:56:02,100 --> 00:56:03,640
 nadam se da je dobar kadar,

1351
00:56:03,820 --> 00:56:05,960
 Petre, ja sam više formacija

1352
00:56:05,960 --> 00:56:07,600
 i rad s članovima zajednice,

1353
00:56:07,600 --> 00:56:08,600
 to se malo i vidi.

1354
00:56:08,600 --> 00:56:12,400
 Meni je konačno stigla u ruke

1355
00:56:12,400 --> 00:56:14,340
 knjiga za sve.

1356
00:56:15,440 --> 00:56:16,580
 nešto hrvatsko,

1357
00:56:16,580 --> 00:56:18,840
 nešto karizmatsko,

1358
00:56:18,840 --> 00:56:20,080
 katoličko,

1359
00:56:20,080 --> 00:56:21,580
 sigurno, zdravo,

1360
00:56:21,580 --> 00:56:24,160
 knjigu koju ću sigurno koristiti

1361
00:56:24,160 --> 00:56:25,080
 u svom radu

1362
00:56:25,080 --> 00:56:27,180
 i u formaciji naših članova.

1363
00:56:27,180 --> 00:56:29,400
 I zato vam toplo preporučam,

1364
00:56:29,400 --> 00:56:30,820
 ne samo voditeljima,

1365
00:56:30,820 --> 00:56:32,800
 nego svima da uzmete tu knjigu

1366
00:56:32,800 --> 00:56:34,980
 i da je stavite na svoje police

1367
00:56:34,980 --> 00:56:37,800
 i zvano imate čovjeka za pročitat.

1368
00:56:37,800 --> 00:56:39,320
 Hvala.

1369
00:56:39,320 --> 00:56:48,340
 Nije rekla da će ovo reći.

1370
00:56:48,340 --> 00:56:50,020
 Bilo je drugo,

1371
00:56:50,020 --> 00:56:50,760
 trebala reći,

1372
00:56:50,760 --> 00:56:51,260
 ali dobro je.

1373
00:56:51,260 --> 00:56:53,060
 Hvala ti, Anita.

1374
00:56:53,060 --> 00:56:54,940
 Hvala ti.

1375
00:56:54,940 --> 00:56:59,380
 Volio bi da jedan čovjek,

1376
00:56:59,380 --> 00:57:01,200
 moj osobni psihijatar,

1377
00:57:01,200 --> 00:57:03,460
 Lovro Uglešić,

1378
00:57:03,460 --> 00:57:04,560
 gdje si, Lovro?

1379
00:57:04,560 --> 00:57:05,400
 Dođi brzo,

1380
00:57:05,400 --> 00:57:06,700
 nemam puno vremena,

1381
00:57:06,700 --> 00:57:08,700
 imamo 10-11 minuta.

1382
00:57:09,320 --> 00:57:11,120
 Mi smo vam sjedili za tim stolom

1383
00:57:11,120 --> 00:57:11,940
 kao voditelji.

1384
00:57:11,940 --> 00:57:14,100
 Bilo je suza,

1385
00:57:14,100 --> 00:57:15,080
 bilo je čuđenja,

1386
00:57:15,080 --> 00:57:15,860
 bilo je svega.

1387
00:57:15,860 --> 00:57:19,620
 I za vrijeme tih molitvi,

1388
00:57:19,620 --> 00:57:21,420
 znači prije nego što je bilo

1389
00:57:21,420 --> 00:57:22,400
 prvo Međugorje,

1390
00:57:22,400 --> 00:57:23,700
 prije 11 godina,

1391
00:57:23,700 --> 00:57:26,660
 smo znali dobijati neke pjesme.

1392
00:57:26,660 --> 00:57:29,060
 Neke pjesme smo dobijali

1393
00:57:29,060 --> 00:57:30,960
 i tako smo dobili pjesmu

1394
00:57:30,960 --> 00:57:34,280
 koju ćemo sad upotrijebiti

1395
00:57:34,280 --> 00:57:35,320
 kao način molitve.

1396
00:57:35,320 --> 00:57:37,620
 Došla je kao karizma zajedništva,

1397
00:57:38,080 --> 00:57:39,380
 a da ne znamo da se radi

1398
00:57:39,380 --> 00:57:40,600
 o karizmi zajedništva.

1399
00:57:40,600 --> 00:57:43,480
 I mi ćemo evo tu autentičnu

1400
00:57:43,480 --> 00:57:45,320
 jednu melodiju iskoristiti

1401
00:57:45,320 --> 00:57:47,640
 da pokušamo evo po prvi put

1402
00:57:47,640 --> 00:57:50,560
 čutije i ući kroz nju.

1403
00:57:50,560 --> 00:57:52,660
 Kao onda kad mi nismo znali šta je,

1404
00:57:52,660 --> 00:57:53,880
 a dobili smo tu karizmu,

1405
00:57:53,880 --> 00:57:55,880
 da sad zajedno svi pokušamo ući

1406
00:57:55,880 --> 00:57:57,460
 s tom pjesmom

1407
00:57:57,460 --> 00:58:00,020
 u duhovno stanje,

1408
00:58:00,020 --> 00:58:01,520
 šta Bog od nas radi.

1409
00:58:02,160 --> 00:58:03,640
 pjesma se zove Hram,

1410
00:58:03,640 --> 00:58:05,480
 tako je nekako došla

1411
00:58:05,480 --> 00:58:08,380
 i došla je odjedan put refren.

1412
00:58:08,380 --> 00:58:11,020
 Ostali su dijelovi dolazili pomalo

1413
00:58:11,020 --> 00:58:12,280
 kao bljeskovi,

1414
00:58:12,280 --> 00:58:15,040
 ali je došla kao jedan refren

1415
00:58:15,040 --> 00:58:15,460
 u komadu,

1416
00:58:15,460 --> 00:58:18,420
 tako kako ćete i vi sada čuti.

1417
00:58:19,460 --> 00:58:22,060
 Njena svrha je da ako mi ovdje svi

1418
00:58:22,060 --> 00:58:23,980
 sad zakoračimo još malo više

1419
00:58:23,980 --> 00:58:25,560
 na tom putu ljubavi,

1420
00:58:25,560 --> 00:58:27,280
 ona je svoje ispunila.

1421
00:58:27,280 --> 00:58:30,040
 I zato evo vas pozivam

1422
00:58:30,040 --> 00:58:31,700
 da možete ustati,

1423
00:58:31,700 --> 00:58:33,400
 da ćemo sada moliti

1424
00:58:33,400 --> 00:58:34,580
 i slaviti.

1425
00:58:34,580 --> 00:58:37,760
 Prvo bi bilo dobro

1426
00:58:37,760 --> 00:58:39,840
 da staviš Valentin onaj

1427
00:58:39,840 --> 00:58:42,060
 Lovre, hoćemo refren.

1428
00:58:42,060 --> 00:58:43,740
 Lovre.

1429
00:58:43,740 --> 00:58:45,620
 Refren, je li tako?

1430
00:58:45,620 --> 00:58:46,660
 Dobro.

1431
00:58:46,660 --> 00:58:49,000
 Uvježbaćemo refren.

1432
00:58:49,460 --> 00:58:50,600
 Prvo, svi zajedno,

1433
00:58:50,600 --> 00:58:51,520
 pošto je cilj

1434
00:58:51,520 --> 00:58:54,420
 da pjevajući i čitajući riječi

1435
00:58:54,420 --> 00:58:55,920
 molimo.

1436
00:58:55,920 --> 00:58:58,520
 Da molimo zajedno.

1437
00:58:58,520 --> 00:59:01,740
 Radi se o tome

1438
00:59:01,740 --> 00:59:03,660
 kako gospodin pali plam

1439
00:59:03,660 --> 00:59:04,860
 u našim srcima

1440
00:59:04,860 --> 00:59:07,880
 i kako mu dajemo hvalu i slavu

1441
00:59:07,880 --> 00:59:10,980
 na tome što čini sa svima nama.

1442
00:59:10,980 --> 00:59:12,120
 Evo, molio bi,

1443
00:59:12,120 --> 00:59:13,180
 bilo bi dobro,

1444
00:59:13,180 --> 00:59:15,040
 voditelji koji su tada bili,

1445
00:59:15,040 --> 00:59:17,380
 su tu i Hrvoje,

1446
00:59:17,380 --> 00:59:19,000
 i Tomislav,

1447
00:59:19,220 --> 00:59:19,960
 i Tonči,

1448
00:59:19,960 --> 00:59:21,020
 i Robi.

1449
00:59:21,020 --> 00:59:22,600
 Bilo je još sad,

1450
00:59:22,600 --> 00:59:23,480
